name: Project Euler
body:
## Welcome to my solutions to some Project Euler problems.
I'll be posting my solutions to some project Euler problems in this repo.  **Spoiler alert**, they work so don't check them unless you want to see how I solved the problem.

###Language choice
I'll be solving problems in languages I'm familiar with, and use frequently, so you'll probably see solutions in less 'typical' languages (Javascript for starters).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
